	<div class="commentBody">
		<div id="comment_body_65149975"><p>STOP HAVING EVERY DAMN THING NEED INTERNET ACCESS.</p><p>For fuck's sake, let's have a standard where all your devices use non-routing protocols and have to connect to a local server before a connection to the world can be established.</p><p>Now you have only one central device to keep updated, and 90% of its job is, from the very beginning, to keep those other devices isolated and protected.</p></div>
	</div>

